  "06bd7a64-5fb2-ae4d-aeae-50f02a2cbdf3"],
 ", which is consistent with the equation found in Jagjits notebook. Using \
this we can define our overlap elements by symmetry as \n",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{
