r}\\left(r^{2}\\frac{\\partial}{\\partial r}\\Phi_{j}(r)\\right)", "state" -> 
     "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "7192e509-9567-5143-bf4d-5bac0f0ddb72"],
 ". We define the reduced radial wavefunction as ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{
         FractionBox[
          RowBox[{
            SubscriptBox[
             StyleBox["u", "TI"], 
             StyleBox["i", "TI"]], "(", 
            StyleBox["r", "TI"], ")"}], 
          StyleBox["r", "TI"]], "\[LongEqual]", 
         SubscriptBox["\[CapitalPhi]", 
          StyleBox["i", "TI"]], 
         RowBox[{"(", 
