\\frac{u_{i}(r)}{r}\\left(\\frac{du_{k}(r)}{dr}+r\\frac{d^{2}u_{k}(r)}{dr^{2}}\
- \\frac{du_{k}(r)}{dr}\\right)=\\int_{0}^{\\infty}dr \
u_{i}(r)\\frac{d^{2}u_{k}(r)}{dr^{2}}", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
    "TeXAssistantTemplate"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "8df84fb3-7932-084f-9677-daa4e56a58aa"],
 ".\nIntegrating this by parts and using the boundary conditions that ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   TemplateBox[<|"boxes" -> FormBox[
       RowBox[{
         StyleBox["u", "TI"], 
         RowBox[{"(", "0", ")"}], "\[LongEqual]", "0", ",", 
         StyleBox["u", "TI"], 
